data.description: Welcome to 215 Camlau Dr #D, a renovated condo in the sought-after Summerwind community of Chula Vista.  In 2020, this unit was updated with kitchen appliances, new flooring, and baseboards, giving it a fresh and contemporary look.  In the living room, a wood-burning fireplace provides a cozy ambiance. A large sliding glass door leads to a sizable balcony off where you have open views overlooking the community pool, offering a relaxing retreat and space to grill.  The south-facing windowed kitchen is brightly lit and well appointed with appliances by Whirlpool, LG, and Frigidaire. There is ample cabinet space, and it features an open layout and breakfast bar, facilitating easy meal preparation and entertaining.  This condo features a split-two bedroom design, with each bedroom and bathroom located on opposite sides of the home. Bedroom windows face to the north and provide open views of the community.  For parking convenience, this home includes two spaces - a one-car detached garage and a separate assigned outdoor parking space. The building is VA financing approved.  Situated in the desirable Summerwind community, you'll appreciate the spaciousness of the condos in this development. The HOA includes water, trash, parking, and access to the common area amenities.   Enjoy proximity to highly-rated Hilltop Park and Trail for outdoor gatherings and hiking, major shopping centers such as the Chula Vista Center, outstanding dining options, and easy access to major freeways for convenient commuting throughout San Diego County.
